Abstract: This assignment has had a journey. I attempted to add two new images(mainly with incredibly content white guys in suits). I'm not sure that they were successfully appended. That being said, I'm wishing this assignment a brand new day. I have taken out the Sting video, though it would be neat to include it for thirteen seconds in a future iteration(see what I did there?) 
I attempted to parse long-winded paragraphs that sounded like they were talking down to the potential customer. Entitled dudes with companies don't want to hear the extensive details. They don't have time. They're working presumedly on billable hours. Therefore, I made everything as concise as physically possible, with a positive spin(and really, everybody likes Sting). 
I am putting this assignment to bed. 
